@description.name: @description
@description.body: Static helper functions for arrays with a lot of often used convenience methods like remove or contains. The native JavaScript Array is not modified by this class. However, there are modifications to the native Array in {@link qx.lang.normalize.Array} for browsers that do not support certain JavaScript features natively .
